Class GenericTableModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
      • com.cafean.client.values.util.ClipboardTableModel
        • com.cafean.client.ui.GenericTableModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AddRowsInterface, SortableModel, java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.table.TableModel
    public class GenericTableModel
extends ClipboardTableModel
    A generic implementation of a ClipboardTableModel. This table model uses a List of GenericTMColumn to implement the table model interface.
